name: Recognize
description:
Recognize text from image


How to use

  1. Select an image with text
  2. Select a language
  3. The recognized text appears to the right of the image


Supported language

Latin (Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch, English, Finnish, French, German, Hungarian, Italian, Polish, Portuguese, Slovenian, Spanish, Swedish, Turkish)

Arabic

Bulgarian

Chinese

Greek

Korean

Japanese

Russian


Artwork by Alice Spoon
